        </div>
        <div class="accordion-content">
          <div class="accordion-body">
            Our standard delivery hours are from 9:00 AM to 6:00 PM, Monday through Friday, and 10:00 AM to 4:00 PM on Saturdays. For businesses with special requirements, we offer flexible delivery windows that can be arranged in advance.
          </div>
