        </div>
        <div class="accordion-content">
          <div class="accordion-body">
            You can schedule a pickup through our website or mobile app. Simply log in to your account, enter the shipment details, and select a convenient pickup time. You can also call our customer service to arrange a pickup. For regular pickups, we offer scheduled pickup services that can be customized to your business needs.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="accordion">
        <div class="accordion-header">
          <div class="accordion-title">What is the estimated delivery time for domestic shipments?</div>
          <div class="accordion-icon"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-content">
          <div class="accordion-body">
            Delivery times for domestic shipments vary based on the service selected and the distance between the origin and destination. Our Express service typically delivers within 1-2 business days, while our Standard service delivers within 2-5 business days. Same-day delivery is available in select cities for orders placed before 11:00 AM.
